26
00:03:20,012 --> 00:03:23,098
You sound weird. I guess
I'll see you
in a couple of hours.

27
00:03:23,098 --> 00:03:26,226
Yeah, I'll see you
when you get back. Love you.

28
00:03:27,186 --> 00:03:28,812
