37
00:03:56,924 --> 00:03:58,467
Oh, yeah. Good idea. Do that.

38
00:03:58,467 --> 00:04:00,511
Yeah. What's your name?

39
00:04:00,511 --> 00:04:01,804
- Lucia.
- Greco.

40
00:04:01,804 --> 00:04:04,014
Lucia Greco. Perfect.

41
00:04:04,932 --> 00:04:07,101
Okay, let's go.

42
00:04:07,101 --> 00:04:09,937
Choo-choo! Here we go. Okay.

43
00:04:09,937 --> 00:04:13,190
<i>Grazie mille.</i> And, um,
