<i>- Ciao,</i> Rocco.

49
00:04:47,641 --> 00:04:49,143
<i>Ciao,</i> Valentina.

50
00:04:49,143 --> 00:04:51,729
- <i>Ciao.</i>
- <i>Ciao,</i> Isabella.

51
00:05:02,865 --> 00:05:04,867
Happy to take them off you.
- Thank you.

52
00:05:11,665 --> 00:05:12,666
No.

53
00:05:14,835 --> 00:05:15,836
Ah.

54
00:05:33,979 --> 00:05:36,607
