65
00:05:57,002 --> 00:05:59,546
It's very near,
and it's very nice.

66
00:05:59,546 --> 00:06:00,881
Great. <i>Grazie.</i>

67
00:06:00,881 --> 00:06:02,466
- You're welcome.
<i>- Prego.</i>

68
00:06:05,844 --> 00:06:06,929
