81
00:07:02,067 --> 00:07:03,986
I'm sorry that I was...

82
00:07:03,986 --> 00:07:05,863
I don't know why...
Just-- Last night was...

83
00:07:05,863 --> 00:07:09,032
No. It's-- it's fine.
Don't-- don't be sorry.

84
00:07:09,032 --> 00:07:12,953
Yeah. Uh, we should
definitely hang out today.

85
00:07:12,953 --> 00:07:15,706
Okay. Yeah. That'd be fun.

86
00:07:15,706 --> 00:07:18,083
Yeah, I--
I just have to get out

87
