88
00:07:25,007 --> 00:07:26,508
It's been a lot.

89
00:07:26,508 --> 00:07:29,428
I just have to deal with that.
And then, um...

90
00:07:29,428 --> 00:07:32,431
Yeah, maybe we can, like,
plan something after breakfast.

91
00:07:32,431 --> 00:07:33,640
Okay. Good luck.

92
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:34,850
- Cool.
- Okay.

93
00:07:34,850 --> 00:07:36,643
See you in a bit. Bye.

94
00:07:40,856 --> 00:07:43,609
So, I know I'm,
like, on the clock,

95
00:07:43,609 --> 00:07:44,943
