100
00:08:03,253 --> 00:08:05,339
Yeah, I just mess everything up.

101
00:08:05,339 --> 00:08:06,840
I feel like
if I won the lottery,

102
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:08,217
I'd throw away the ticket.

103
00:08:09,718 --> 00:08:11,595
So, I just feel like I...

104
00:08:11,595 --> 00:08:13,889
should give him a chance,
you know?

105
00:08:16,391 --> 00:08:19,519
♪ (EERIE MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

106
00:08:25,150 --> 00:08:27,277
I don't know what's going on
