109
00:08:43,001 --> 00:08:46,546
♪ (MUSIC CONCLUDES) ♪

110
00:08:47,297 --> 00:08:48,757
So chic.

111
00:08:48,757 --> 00:08:50,717
Oh, oh...

112
00:08:51,468 --> 00:08:52,761
Thank you.

113
00:08:52,761 --> 00:08:54,179
You have impeccable style.

114
00:08:54,179 --> 00:08:55,597
The moment
I saw you last night,

115
00:08:55,597 --> 00:08:59,101
