No, no. Ah, Lucia.

145
00:11:28,792 --> 00:11:30,460
Oh!

146
00:11:30,460 --> 00:11:32,421
Luci.
Mount Etna.

147
00:11:33,422 --> 00:11:35,090
We should climb it.

148
00:11:35,090 --> 00:11:36,883
Not sure you're up
