161
00:12:24,306 --> 00:12:26,266
Come on. We had fun.

162
00:12:30,979 --> 00:12:32,063
Bro code?

163
00:12:33,106 --> 00:12:34,733
Bro code?

164
00:12:34,733 --> 00:12:36,193
Yeah, baby, bro code.

165
00:12:37,444 --> 00:12:39,863
Sure, yeah, whatever. Bro code.

166
00:12:40,947 --> 00:12:42,073
Thank you.

167
