198
00:14:55,624 --> 00:14:57,834
Oh, your dad and I
can join you for lunch.

199
00:14:57,834 --> 00:14:59,753
Uh, maybe.
I was kinda thinking

200
00:14:59,753 --> 00:15:02,672
