214
00:15:53,056 --> 00:15:54,683
Come back around and up.

215
00:15:58,978 --> 00:15:59,979
Okay.

216
00:16:04,859 --> 00:16:06,903
<i>Bellissima.</i> Sorry,
I'm already drunk.

217
00:16:06,903 --> 00:16:09,072
Hello.

218
00:16:09,072 --> 00:16:10,699
What can I get you to drink?

219
00:16:10,699 --> 00:16:12,200
Wow, yeah. Um, okay.

220
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:13,910
All right here. Okay.

221
00:16:13,910 --> 00:16:15,662
I'm gonna have
some rosé if you have it.

222
00:16:15,662 --> 00:16:16,830
