- ...Hugo and Didier.

226
00:16:24,671 --> 00:16:25,714
- Hello.
- Hey.

227
00:16:25,714 --> 00:16:27,799
<i>- Bonjour, bonjour, bonjour.</i>
- Hi.

228
00:16:27,799 --> 00:16:29,676
- You're French, right?
- Yes!

229
00:16:29,676 --> 00:16:31,720
Oh, my gosh.

230
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:34,389
Didier's family have the most
