244
00:17:02,917 --> 00:17:05,420
Um, I-- I don't know.
I haven't been in it.

245
00:17:05,420 --> 00:17:08,131
Should we get some <i>panelle,</i>
some <i>fritto misto?</i>

246
00:17:08,131 --> 00:17:10,592
Finger food is always a must. Anyway...

247
00:17:10,592 --> 00:17:11,760
- Oh! Thank you.
- Oh, thank you.

248
00:17:12,177 --> 00:17:13,178
Thank you.

249
00:17:13,178 --> 00:17:14,345
- That's it!
- Let's go.

250
00:17:14,345 --> 00:17:15,513
